%20private%20gym%20make%20life%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Harrison%20Granger%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20account%20executive%20in%20Dubai.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20working%20as%20a%20recruitment%20consultant%20in%20my%20hometown%20of%20Maidstone%20in%20Kent%2C%20England%2C%20for%20five%20years%20when%20I%20decided%20I%20was%20ready%20for%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20move%20on%20and%20progress%20in%20my%20career.%20I%20decided%20to%20not%20only%20swap%20jobs%20but%20also%20move%20countries%20and%20try%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20and%20we%20love%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20first%20memory%20of%20Dubai%20is%20visiting%20my%20uncle%20with%20my%20parents%20as%20a%20child%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20talked%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-tax-safety-security-top-cities-workation-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20abroad%2C%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E%20quickly%20became%20one%20of%20our%20top%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20my%20uncle%20who%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-live-dubai-qatar-teacher-salary-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20at%20the%20beach%20or%20the%20waterparks.%20I%20also%20remember%20being%20amazed%20sharks%20were%20swimming%20in%20a%20tank%20in%20the%20mall.%20Sometimes%2C%20now%20that%20we%20live%20here%2C%20I'll%20take%20my%20laptop%20and%20work%20in%20the%20nearby%20caf%C3%A9%20that%20has%20the%20aquarium%20as%20its%20backdrop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20in%20the%20summer%20because%20I%20thought%20that%20as%20a%20Brit%20who's%20not%20used%20to%20any%20heat%2C%20we%20might%20as%20well%20get%20acclimated%20to%20the%20country%20when%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-indoors-climate-change-future-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehottest%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20were%20coming%20from%20the%20Kent%20countryside%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Garden%20of%20England%2C%20my%20partner%20wasn't%20initially%20sure%20if%20she%20would%20enjoy%20the%20city%20life%20surrounded%20by%20skyscrapers.%20Now%20she%20loves%20it%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20move%20closer%20to%20downtown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecuring%20jobs%20was%20a%20challenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20shock%20happened%20when%20the%20job%20my%20partner%20had%20lined%20up%20in%20the%20recruitment%20industry%20fell%20through.%20We%20planned%20for%20her%20to%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-spend-six-figure-salary-gen-z-millennials-jobs-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emain%20money%20earner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I'd%20find%20a%20job%20once%20we'd%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20live%20and%20work%20here%2C%20you%20must%20have%20a%20work%20and%20residency%20permit%2C%20which%20your%20company%20will%20apply%20for%20on%20your%20behalf.%20Luckily%2C%20someone%20from%20my%20uncle's%20events%20company%20left%20when%20we%20moved%2C%20and%20my%20uncle%20asked%20whether%20I%20would%20like%20to%20try%20out%20for%20an%20account-executive%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%20With%20my%20experience%20in%20recruitment%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20show%20what%20I've%20done%20%E2%80%94%20saying%20I've%20placed%20three%20truck%20drivers%20doesn't%20mean%20much%20to%20anyone.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20something%20where%20I%20had%20a%20product%20to%20show%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20working%20in%20events%2C%20I%20can%20show%20people%20photographs%20of%20what%20I've%20been%20up%20to%20for%20the%20past%20three%20months.%20I%20may%20work%20through%20the%20night%20sometimes%2C%20but%20I%20can%20have%20the%20next%20day%20off%20or%20work%20from%20home.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnews-today-november-18-work-life-balance-job-careers-remote-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20much%20better%20in%20Dubai%20than%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20now%20works%20in%20real%20estate.%20We%20both%20earn%20more%20than%20we%20did%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20an%20apartment%20was%20also%20difficult%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-price-outlook-housing-market-real-estate-bubble-inflation-ubs-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20real-estate%20market%20is%20thriving%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20prices%20are%20high.%20Before%20we%20arrived%20in%20Dubai%2C%20we%20saw%20an%20apartment%20online%20in%20the%20Dubai%20Marina%20for%2070%2C000%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20Dirhams%2C%20or%20about%20%2419%2C000%2C%20a%20year%2C%20but%20now%20you're%20lucky%20if%20you%20can%20get%20one%20for%20%2427%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20that%20area.%20Many%20landlords%20here%20request%20the%20full%20amount%20in%20six%20or%20even%20two%20checks%20instead%20of%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20searched%20on%20Dubizzle%20and%20Property%20Finder%20and%20whittled%20down%20our%20list%20to%20only%20landlords%20who%20would%20accept%2012%20checks.%20This%20was%20a%20huge%20help.%20We%20also%20weren't%20clear%20on%20where%20we%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20Dubai%2C%20so%20we%20cast%20our%20net%20wider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20a%20place%20this%20way%2C%20and%20we%20pay%20about%20%2416%2C800%20a%20year%2C%20including%20bills%2C%20for%20a%20fully%20furnished%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Dubai%20Production%20City.%20It's%20in%20one%20of%20the%20cheaper%20areas%20of%20the%20city%2C%20but%20my%20friends%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20still%20amazed%20to%20find%20out%20that%20the%20apartment%20block%20features%20a%20private%20gym%2C%20swimming%20pool%2C%20and%20tennis%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20belong%20to%20a%20health%20club%20in%20Kent%2C%20where%20I%20would%20pay%20about%20%24130%20a%20month%20for%20access%20to%20similar%20facilities.%20Now%20it's%20included%20in%20my%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryday%20life%20is%20so%20much%20easier%20than%20it%20was%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Dubai%20is%20so%20Western%2C%20I%20haven't%20had%20any%20problems%20getting%20my%20bearings%20in%20my%20new%20home%2C%20but%20driving%20on%20Dubai's%20roads%20was%20one%20of%20my%20biggest%20learning%20curves.%20It's%20a%20lot%20more%20aggressive%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20road%20rage.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20drive%20with%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20had%20to%20visit%20a%20gas%20station%20since%20I've%20lived%20in%20Dubai.%20There's%20a%20gas-delivery%20app%20called%20Cafu%20I%20use.%20I%20place%20an%20order%20online%2C%20and%20it%20sends%20a%20tanker%20to%20your%20home%20and%20fills%20up%20your%20car%20overnight.%20Filling%20up%20my%20car%20in%20the%20UK%20cost%20about%20%2490.%20It's%20half%20that%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20in%20Dubai%20is%20priced%20similarly%20to%20that%20in%20the%20UK.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20apps%20on%20which%20you%20can%20order%20food.%20With%20some%20apps%2C%20you%20can%20order%20a%20few%20groceries%20before%20you%20sit%20down%20to%20dinner%2C%20and%20they'll%20arrive%20before%20you%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20is%20also%20super%20safe.%20When%20we%20left%20the%20office%20one%20night%2C%20my%20colleagues%20tried%20to%20get%20in%20my%20car%2C%20and%20they%20were%20shocked%20it%20was%20locked.%20I%20always%20locked%20my%20car%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20things%20I%20miss%3C%2Fs