logic%20controls%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704445260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0tmac8e8_tesla_625x300_17_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-to-recall-1-6-million-electric-cars-in-china-to-fix-steering-software-regulator-4804700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20is%20recalling%20more%20than%201.6%20million%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20China%2C%20the%20country's%20market%20regulator%20said%20Friday%2C%20owing%20to%20software%20issues%20that%20could%20pose%20safety%20risks%20while%20driving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-to-recall-1-6-million-electric-cars-in-china-to-fix-steering-software-regulator-4804700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-to-recall-1-6-million-electric-cars-in-china-to-fix-steering-software-regulator-4804700%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-to-recall-1-6-million-electric-cars-in-china-to-fix-steering-software-regulator-4804700%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Prayer%20for%20Jimmy%20Lai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05134056%2FJimmy_Lai_go_to_The_Court_of_Final_Appeal_20201231.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20Jimmy%20Lai%20in%20shackles%20entering%20a%20Hong%20Kong%20courtroom%20this%20week%20was%20a%20shock%20for%20me%20on%20a%20personal%20level.%20I%E2%80%99d%20gotten%20to%20know%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20media%20mogul%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20pro-democracy%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EApple%20Daily%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20when%20I%20worked%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20Hong%20Kong%20bureau.%20He%20was%2C%20pardon%20the%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20larger%20than%20life%20%E2%80%93%20a%20bear%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20gentle%20spirit%20whose%20passion%20for%20democracy%20was%20equaled%20only%20by%20his%20commitment%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20a%20self-made%20man%2C%20unlike%20many%20mainland%20millionaires%20who%20owe%20their%20fortunes%20to%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20connections.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2012%2C%20Jimmy%20stowed%20away%20on%20a%20ship%20headed%20from%20the%20mainland%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20went%20to%20work%20in%20the%20garment%20industry.%20A%20brilliant%20apprentice%2C%20he%20moved%20up%20the%20ranks%2C%20became%20a%20manager%2C%20owner%2C%20and%20eventually%20the%20CEO%20and%20president%20of%20a%20multinational%20clothing%20and%20retail%20empire%2C%20Giordano%2C%20which%20at%20its%20peak%20had%20outlets%20across%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJimmy%20eventually%20sold%20off%20most%20of%20his%20garment%20and%20retail%20interests%20to%20launch%20media%20outlets%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ENext%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201990%20and%20the%20hugely%20popular%20%3Cem%3EApple%20Daily%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20in%201995%2C%20both%20of%20which%20had%20a%20hard-hitting%20reporting%20and%20editorial%20style%20that%20championed%20democracy%20and%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20afraid%20to%20take%20on%20Beijing%20or%20those%20who%20kowtowed%20to%20the%20CCP%20in%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20political%20and%20business%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%20was%20at%20his%20home%20or%20a%20favourite%20Hong%20Kong%20restaurant%2C%20whenever%20we%20met%20there%20was%20usually%20a%20meal%20involved%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20appetite%20for%20good%20food%20and%20drink%20was%20nearly%20as%20voracious%20as%20his%20appetite%20for%20conversation%20and%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20first%20met%20Jimmy%20in%201998%2C%20the%20year%20after%20Hong%20Kong%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Chandover%E2%80%9D%20from%20Britain%20to%20Beijing%2C%20and%20our%20meetings%20%E2%80%93%20often%20with%20other%20members%20of%20the%20press%2C%20academics%2C%20local%20politicians%2C%20and%20human-rights%20activists%20%E2%80%93%20would%20inevitably%20turn%20to%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20mainland%20was%20undermining%20its%20%E2%80%9Cone%20country%2C%20two%20systems%E2%80%9D%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20devout%20Catholic%2C%20Jimmy%E2%80%99s%20faith%20was%20%E2%80%93%20and%20is%20%E2%80%93%20central%20to%20his%20identity%2C%20and%20we%20were%20frequently%20joined%20by%20local%20clergy%20around%20a%20big%20table%2C%20where%20Jimmy%2C%20while%20generously%20listening%20to%20all%20present%2C%20held%20court.%20His%20stories%2C%20often%20filled%20with%20outrage%20over%20injustices%20done%20to%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20people%2C%20ranged%20from%20the%20Japanese%20occupation%20during%20World%20War%20II%20to%20the%20riots%20against%20British%20colonial%20rule%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20and%20the%20threat%20to%20judicial%20independence%20after%201997.%20But%20they%20were%20also%20filled%20with%20goodwill%2C%20humour%2C%20and%20Jimmy%E2%80%99s%20bedrock%20belief%20that%20we%2C%20as%20his%20faith%20teaches%2C%20should%20%E2%80%9CDo%20unto%20others%20as%20we%20would%20have%20them%20do%20unto%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20I%20looked%20up%20to%20Jimmy.%20He%20was%20to%20me%20%E2%80%93%20a%20young%20journalist%20on%20my%20first%20real%20overseas%20assignment%20%E2%80%93%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20freedoms%20that%20the%20great%20majority%20of%20Hong%20Kongers%20cherished%2C%20and%20an%20example%20of%20why%20the%20%E2%80%9Cone%20country%2C%20two%20systems%E2%80%9D%20promise%20made%20by%20Beijing%20in%201997%20was%20so%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20promise%20was%20supposed%20to%20last%20at%20least%2050%20years%2C%20until%202047%2C%20over%20which%20time%20Hong%20Kong%20would%20gradually%20expand%20its%20citizens%E2%80%99democratic%20rights.%20Sadly%2C%20that%20promise%20was%20shattered%2C%20along%20with%20the%20lives%20of%20Jimmy%20Lai%20and%20thousands%20of%20other%20lesser-known%20activists%2C%20in%20a%20brutal%20crackdown%20by%20craven%20Hong%20Kong%20authorities%20under%20the%20sway%20of%20Communist%20Party%20leaders%20in%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisibly%20thinner%20and%20fatigued%20after%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20days%20behind%20bars%2C%20Jimmy%2C%20who%20turned%2076%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20is%20currently%20imprisoned%20in%20a%20maximum-security%20cell%20under%20bogus%20%E2%80%9Cfraud%E2%80%9D%20charges.%20He%20now%20faces%20life%20in%20prison%20on%20equally%20ludicrous%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20charges%20of%20publishing%20%E2%80%9Cseditious%20materials%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20any%20honest%20individual%20knows%2C%20it%20is%20not%20Jimmy%20Lai%20but%20those%20who%20do%20the%20bidding%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20in%20Beijing%20that%20are%20the%20true%20threats%20to%20Hong%20Kongers%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20and%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mark%20Clifford%2C%20award-winning%20journalist%20and%20president%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecfhk.org%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Committee%20for%20Freedom%20in%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me%20this%20week%2C%20instead%20of%20living%20up%20to%20the%20promise%20of%20one%20country%2C%20two%20systems%2C%20%E2%80%9CChina%E2%80%99s%20Xi%20Jinping%20demands%20total%20submission.%20Even%20one%20person%20sticking%20up%20is%20like%20a%20nail%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20hammered%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20Clifford%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CJimmy%20is%20not%20your%20average%20nail.%20His%20advocacy%20on%20behalf%20of%20freedom%2C%20his%20advocacy%20for%20the%20democracy%20that%20China%20promised%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20is%20an%20unambiguous%20challenge%20to%20a%20communist%20dictatorship.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20that%20Jimmy%20is%20a%2076-year-old%20man%20who%20has%20always%20preached%20nonviolence.%20He%20dares%20to%20challenge%20Beijing%20through%20his%20commitment%20to%20truth%20and%20by%20having%20strong%20moral%20values%20that%20he%20has%20the%20courage%20to%20live%20and%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%20die%20by.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESebastien%20Lai%2C%20Jimmy%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20who%20was%20just%20a%20young%20boy%20the%20last%20time%20I%20met%20him%2C%20is%20heading%20the%20international%20campaign%20to%20free%20his%20father%2C%20tirelessly%20meeting%20with%20legislators%2C%20human-rights%20organisations%2C%20and%20heads%20of%20state%20around%20the%20globe.%20Writing%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Globe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20this%20week%2C%20Sebastien%2C%20now%2028%2C%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20government%20accused%20my%20father%2C%20Jimmy%20Lai%2C%20of%20charges%20under%20China%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20law%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9Ccolluding%20with%20foreign%20forces%E2%80%9D%20and%20sedition.%20The%20truth%20is%20much%20less%20convoluted.%20For%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20my%20father%20published%20Apple%20Daily%2C%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20largest%20pro-democracy%20newspaper%2C%20and%20was%20one%20of%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20most%20outspoken%20and%20dauntless%20critics.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20authorities%20are%20putting%20on%20an%20elaborate%20show%20to%20discredit%20and%20silence%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOn%20Monday%20morning%2C%20when%20his%20sham%20trial%20finally%20began%20after%20more%20than%201%2C000%20days%20of%20pre-trial%20detention%2C%20sniffer%20dogs%20patrolled%20the%20street%20outside%20of%20West%20Kowloon%20Court%2C%20and%20police%20officers%20deployed%20to%20secure%20the%20area%E2%80%941%2C000%20of%20them%2C%20according%20to%20reports%E2%80%94scanned%20passing%20cars%20for%20bombs.%20Law%20enforcement%20dwarfed%20both%20press%20presence%20and%20the%20crowd%20queueing%20to%20witness%20the%20trial.%20Local%20media%20have%20reported%20that%20the%20same%20show%20of%20force%20will%20be%20deployed%20every%20day%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%2080-day%20trial.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20tight%20security%2C%20like%20the%20trial%20itself%2C%20is%20a%20co-ordinated%20performance%20to%20paint%20him%20as%20a%20dangerous%20man.%20But%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20it%20betrays%20something%20else%3A%20how%20terrified%20tyranny%20is%20of%20defiance%2C%20and%20how%20insecure%20Beijing%20and%20its%20puppets%20are%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20man%20who%20stands%20up%20for%20freedom%20and%20speaks%20truth%20to%20power%2C%20whatever%20the%20cost%20may%20be.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20how%20much%20access%20Jimmy%20has%20to%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20of%20one%20thing%3A%20He%E2%80%99s%20proud%20of%20his%20boy%2C%20Sebastien%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20outcome%20of%20his%20sham%20of%20a%20trial.%20The%20irony%20is%20almost%20too%20painful.%20In%20a%20Kafkaesque%20nightmare%2C%20a%20man%20who%20believes%20in%20truth%20and%20justice%20finds%20himself%20in%20a%20predetermined%20trial%20that%20respects%20neither.%20Yet%2C%20unlike%20Kafka%E2%80%99s%20Josef%20K%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Trial%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jimmy%2C%20like%20Socrates%2C%20has%20lived%20a%20fully%20examined%20life%2C%20guided%20by%20faith%20not%20fear%2C%20truth%20not%20deception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Clifford%2C%20a%20longtime%20friend%20and%20colleague%20of%20Jimmy%E2%80%99s%2C%20explained%20in%20my%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmichaeljudge.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-tragedy-of-hong-kong-and-why%3Fs%3Dw%5C%22%3E%C2%A0TFP%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20him%20last%20year%20upon%20the%20release%20of%20his%20book%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FToday-Hong-Kong-Tomorrow-World%2Fdp%2F1250279178%3Fasc_source%3D01GTER1X19F274KT48MCTDGTQG%26tag%3Dnamespacebran383-20%5C%22%3EToday%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Tomorrow%20the%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20Communist%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Ccrave%20legitimacy%2C%20but%20they%20fear%20their%20own%20people.%20And%20they%20know%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20material%20progress%2C%20building%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20et%20cetera%2C%20their%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20Jimmy%20Lai%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20certainty%20in%20his%20cause%20%E2%80%93%20buoyed%20by%20his%20love%20for%20his%20wife%2C%20Teresa%2C%20his%20children%2C%20and%20his%20Catholic%20faith%20%E2%80%93%20continues%20to%20flourish%2C%20even%20behind%20bars.%20As%20I%20wrote%20in%20my%20interview%20with%20Clifford%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20stirring%20words%20in%20his%20book%20%E2%80%93%20itself%20a%20moving%20testament%20to%20the%20character%20and%20endurance%20of%20Hong%20Kong%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20activists%20%E2%80%93%20weren%E2%80%99t%20written%20by%20the%20author%20but%20by%20Jimmy%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20his%20old%20friend%20and%20fellow%20newspaperman%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%E2%80%99m%20adjusting%20very%20well%20in%20prison.%20Without%20the%20distraction%20of%20the%20world%20I%20can%20concentrate%20on%20reading%20my%20books%2C%20especially%20books%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20%5Bbefore%5D%2C%20I%20can%20understand%20now.%20It%E2%80%99s%20such%20a%20joy.%20My%20family%2C%20colleagues%2C%20and%20friends%20and%20even%20people%20here%20have%20been%20very%20supportive.%20I%20know%20I%20must%20have%20done%20the%20right%20thing.%20The%20Lord%20has%20rewarded%20me%20with%20sweet%20joy%20and%20love.%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20used%20to%20think%20I%20love%5Bd%5D%20freedom%20the%20most.%20Now%20I%20know%20I%20love%20Teresa%20the%20most.%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20lucky%20man.%20My%20life%20has%20been%20so%20wonderful.%20I%20can%20face%20whatever%20suffering%20%5Bis%5D%20coming%20forth%20on%20me.%20%E2%80%A6%20Yes%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20enemies.%20But%20funny%20enough%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20hate%2C%20not%20even%20a%20tiny%20bit.%20I%20tell%20myself%20if%20I%20can%20pray%20for%20my%20enemies%20and%20wish%20them%20well%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20have%20no%20fear.%20I%20really%20have%20no%20fear.%20I%20believe%20at%20the%20end%20righteousness%20and%20justice%20will%20prevail.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20New%20Year%2C%20I%20pray%20Jimmy%20is%20right.%20I%20also%20pray%20that%20I%2C%20and%20all%20those%20who%20know%20him%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20his%20family%20and%20loved%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20find%20strength%20in%20the%20courage%20of%20his%20convictions%2C%20and%20peace%20in%20the%20example%20of%20his%20compassion.%20But%20most%20of%20all%20I%20pray%20for%20my%20friend%2C%20that%20he%20may%20return%20to%20the%20loving%20arms%20of%20his%20Teresa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Judge%2C%20a%20former%20deputy%20features%20editor%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3Cem%3E%2C%20is%20a%20US-based%20poet%20and%20freelance%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmichaeljudge.substack.com%2Fp%2Fa-christmas-prayer-for-jimmy-lai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESubstack%20newsletter%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20First%20Person%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704445257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05134056%2FJimmy_Lai_go_to_The_Court_of_Final_Appeal_20201231.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fa-new-years-prayer-for-jimmy-lai%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20any%20honest%20individual%20knows%2C%20it%20is%20not%20Jimmy%20Lai%20but%20those%20who%20do%20the%20bidding%20of%20the%20C