rted%C2%A0suicide%20bombers%20probably%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-what-we-know-about-the-deadly-blasts%2Fa-67889458%5C%22%3Ecarried%20out%20the%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state-run%20IRNA%20news%20agency%20reported%20surveillance%20footage%20from%20the%20route%20to%20the%20commemoration%20at%20Kerman%E2%80%99s%20Martyrs%20Cemetery%20clearly%20showed%20a%20male%20suicide%20bomber%20detonating%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cause%20of%20the%20second%20blast%20was%20most%20likely%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20IRNA%20reported%2C%20quoting%20what%20it%20called%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinformed%20source.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoleimani%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20US%20drone%20attack%20at%20Baghdad%20airport%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20a%20high-ranking%20official%20in%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%C2%A0(IRGC)%20and%20in%20command%20of%20the%20elite%20Quds%20Force%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%E2%80%99s%20campaigns%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20observed%20a%20day%20of%20mourning%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20authorities%20have%20also%20called%20for%20mass%20protests%20on%20Friday%20when%20the%20funerals%20of%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20blasts%20will%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20vows%20revenge%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20%E2%80%9CIS%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20responsibility%2C%20Iranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20and%20inhumane%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20top%20authority%2C%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Khamenei%2C%20vowed%20revenge%20for%20the%20twin%20bombings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIranian%20leader%20vows%20%E2%80%98harsh%20response%E2%80%99%20after%20twin%20blasts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%20data-duration%3D%5C%2201%3A53%5C%22%20data-play-btn-title%3D%5C%22Play%20video%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cpicture%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20Iran%20expert%20at%20United%20Against%20Nuclear%20Iran%2C%20Kasra%20Aarabi%2C%20told%20DW%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20attack%20itself%20certainly%20has%20all%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20ISIS%20operations%20in%20Iran.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20would%20suit%20the%20government%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20regime%20will%20blame%20ISIS%20that%20will%20enable%20the%20%5BIslamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%5D%20IRGC%20to%20respond%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20domestically%20has%20given%20the%20regime%20a%20pretext%20to%20further%20clamp%20down%20on%20the%20Iranian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aarabi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoleimani%20was%20also%20a%20staunch%20enemy%20of%20the%20so-called%20Islamic%20State%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUN%20Security%20Council%20condemns%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Security%20Council%20has%20condemned%20the%20bombings%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccowardly%20terrorist%20attack.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20members%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20reaffirmed%20that%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%20constitutes%20one%20of%20the%20most%20serious%20threats%20to%20international%20peace%20and%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20UN%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20joined%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20several%20countries%2C%20including%C2%A0Germany%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Jordan%2C%20and%20Iraq%2C%20that%20denounced%20the%20blasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fislamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-bombings-in-iran%2Fa-67741932%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20hr