%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Foscar-pistorius-olympian-hero-turned-disgraced-killer-4803537%5C%22%3EOscar%20Pistorius%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20double-amputee%20South%20African%20Olympic%20athlete%2C%20claims%20woke%20up%20as%20he%20thought%20he%20heard%20an%20intruder.%20Pistorius%20grabbed%20his%209mm%20pistol%20from%20under%20his%20bed%2C%20put%20on%20his%20prosthetic%20legs%2C%20went%20toward%20the%20bathroom%2C%20and%20fired%20four%20shots.%20But%20his%20girlfriend%20Reeva%20Steenkamp%20was%20in%20the%20bathroom%20and%20not%20an%20intruder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20when%20he%20called%20out%20to%20Steenkamp%2C%20whom%20he%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20bed%20beside%20him%2C%20that%20he%20realised%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20tragic%20mistake.%20Pistorius%20claims%20he%20immediately%20broke%20down%20the%20locked%20bathroom%20door%20using%20a%20cricket%20bat%2C%20then%20carried%20the%2029-year-old%20model%20downstairs%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20seek%20help.%20Despite%20his%20efforts%2C%20Steenkamp%20died%20in%20his%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20six-time%20Paralympic%20gold%20winner%20told%20the%20court%2C%20in%20his%20defence%20of%20why%20he%20shot%20dead%20his%20girlfriend%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%20in%202013.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%2C%20however%2C%20dispute%20Pistorius'%20version%20of%20events.%20They%20allege%20that%20the%20former%20track%20star%20intentionally%20put%20on%20his%20prosthetic%20legs%2C%20walked%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20where%20Steenkamp%20had%20locked%20herself%20after%20a%20heated%20argument%2C%20and%20shot%20at%20her%20four%20times.%20Three%20bullets%20struck%20Steenkamp%2C%20leading%20to%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistorius%2C%20now%2037%2C%20spent%20about%20eight%20and%20a%20half%20years%20in%20jail%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20months%20under%20home%20arrest%20before%20he%20was%20sentenced%20for%20murder.%20He%20was%20today%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foscar-pistorius-released-from-jail-11-years-after-murdering-girlfriend-4804041%5C%22%3Ereleased%20from%20jail%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20by%20the%20Steenkamp%20family%20lawyer%20on%20Friday%2C%20Reeva's%20mother%20June%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20never%20be%20justice%20if%20your%20loved%20one%20is%20never%20coming%20back%2C%20and%20no%20amount%20of%20time%20served%20will%20bring%20Reeva%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%2C%20who%20remain%20behind%2C%20are%20the%20ones%20serving%20a%20life%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20June%20Steenkamp%20said%2C%20adding%20her%20only%20desire%20was%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20after%20Pistorius'%20release%20on%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20worldwide%20as%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20carbon-fibre%20prosthetics%2C%20Oscar%20Pistorius%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%20as%20a%20condition%20of%20his%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704440160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkj75sdro_oscar-pistorius-reeva-steenkamp_625x300_05_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foscar-pistorius-murder-reeva-steenkamp-accident-or-rage-what-happened-night-oscar-pistorius-murdered-girlfriend-4804246%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oscar%20Pistorius%2C%20the%20double-amputee%20South%20African%20Olympic%20athlete%2C%20was%20today%20released%20from%20jail%20on%20parole%2C%20nearly%2011%20years%20after%20he%20shot%20dead%20his%20girlfriend%20Reeva%20Steenkamp.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foscar-pistorius-murder-reeva-steenkamp-accident-or-rage-what-happened-night-oscar-pistorius-murdered-girlfriend-4804246%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foscar-pistorius-mur