%20has%20spent%20about%20eight%20and%20a%20half%20years%20in%20jail%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20months%20under%20home%20arrest%20before%20he%20was%20sentenced%20for%20murder.%20A%20parole%20board%20in%20November%20decided%20he%20could%20be%20freed%20after%20completing%20more%20than%20half%20his%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20by%20the%20Steenkamp%20family%20lawyer%20on%20Friday%2C%20Reeva's%20mother%20June%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20never%20be%20justice%20if%20your%20loved%20one%20is%20never%20coming%20back%2C%20and%20no%20amount%20of%20time%20served%20will%20bring%20Reeva%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%2C%20who%20remain%20behind%2C%20are%20the%20ones%20serving%20a%20life%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20June%20Steenkamp%20said%2C%20adding%20her%20only%20desire%20was%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20after%20Pistorius'%20release%20on%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20monitoring%20official%20will%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20him%20until%20his%20sentence%20expires%20in%20December%202029%2C%20whom%20Pistorius%20will%20have%20to%20inform%20if%20he%20seeks%20job%20opportunities%20or%20moves%20to%20a%20new%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foscar-pistorius-case-explained-what-happens-to-blade-runner-oscar-pistorius-on-his-release-from-jail-4787457%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%7C%20What%20Happens%20To%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%26quot%3B%20Oscar%20Pistorius%20On%20His%20Release%20From%20Jail%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20required%20to%20continue%20therapy%20on%20anger%20management%20and%20attend%20sessions%20on%20gender-based%20violence%20as%20part%20of%20his%20parole%20conditions%2C%20the%20Steenkamp%20family%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJune%20Steenkamp%20said%20the%20conditions%20imposed%20by%20the%20parole%20board%20had%20affirmed%20her%20belief%20in%20the%20South%20African%20justice%20system%20as%20they%20send%20out%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20gender-based%20violence%20is%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lawyer%20for%20Pistorius%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20his%20release%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20expect%20him%20to%20live%20at%20the%20home%20of%20his%20uncle%20Arnold%20Pistorius%20in%20a%20wealthy%20Pretoria%20suburb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africans%20have%20shown%20mixed%20reactions%20to%20his%20release%2C%20with%20some%20feeling%20he%20has%20served%20his%20time%2C%20while%20others%20see%20his%20punishment%20as%20too%20lenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20paid%20his%20price.%20Let%20him%20rebuild%20his%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20local%20resident%20told%20reporters%20gathered%20outside%20his%20uncle's%20home%20on%20Friday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20Paralympic%20Star%20To%20Convicted%20Murderer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistorius%20was%20once%20the%20darling%20of%20the%20sports%20world%2C%20and%20a%20pioneering%20voice%20for%20disabled%20athletes%2C%20for%20whom%20he%20campaigned%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20compete%20with%20able-bodied%20participants%20at%20major%20sports%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202012%2C%20mere%20months%20before%20shooting%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20Pistorius%20became%20the%20first%20double%20amputee%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20London%20Olympics%2C%20where%20he%20made%20it%20to%20the%20400%20metres%20semi-finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20won%20two%20gold%20medals%20at%20the%20Paralympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20first%20jailed%20for%20five%20years%20in%20October%202014%20for%20culpable%20homicide%20by%20a%20high%20court.%20After%20his%20prosecutors%20appealed%20that%20ruling%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20found%20him%20guilty%20of%20murder%20in%20December%202015.%20But%20he%20only%20got%20six%20years%20when%20he%20was%20sentenced%20in%20July%202016%2C%20despite%20prosecutors%20arguing%20for%20a%20minimum%20sentence%20of%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20November%202017%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20more%20than%20doubled%20his%20sentence%20to%2013%20years%20and%20five%20months%2C%20describing%20his%20earlier%20term%20as%20%26quot%3Bshockingly%20lenient%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistorius%20met%20Reeva's%20father%20Barry%20Steenkamp%20in%202022%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictim-offender%20dialogue%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20South%20Africa's%20restorative%20justice%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20partly%20on%20how%20indigenous%20cultures%20handled%20crime%20long%20before%20Europeans%20colonised%20South%20Africa%2C%20restorative%20justice%20aims%20to%20find%20closure%20for%20affected%20parties%20in%20a%20crime%2C%20instead%20of%20merely%20punishing%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20initially%20denied%20parole%20in%20March.%20However%2C%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%20subsequently%20ruled%20he%20had%20completed%20half%20of%20his%20sentence%20by%20March%2021%20and%20was%20eligible%20for%20parole%20after%20it%20was%20backdated%20to%20July%202016%20when%20he%20was%20first%20sentenced%20for%20murder%20instead%20of%20November%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704438060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-12%2Foscar-pistorius-afp_650x400_71449562787.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foscar-pistorius-released-from-jail-11-years-after-murdering-girlfriend-4804041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22South%20African%20former%20Paralympic%20star%20Oscar%20Pistorius%20was%20released%20on%20parole%20on%20Friday%2C%20nearly%2011%20years%20after%20murdering%20his%20girlfriend%20in%20a%20crime%20that%20shocked%20a%20nation%20long%20inured%20to%20violence%20against%20women.%22%2C%22autho