Y.S.%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy.%20She%20went%20ahead%20with%20her%20political%20activity%20without%20disturbing%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20position%20in%20spite%20of%20rumblings%20within%20the%20family%20that%20came%20to%20light%20after%20Sharmila%20floated%20her%20own%20party%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ENonetheless%2C%20Sharmila%20is%20joining%20the%20Congress%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20party%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20collapse%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20party%20forfeited%20deposit%20in%20all%20seats%20where%20it%20contested%20in%202014%20and%202019%20assembly%20and%20general%20elections.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20her%20joining%20the%20Congress%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20the%20party%20and%20herself%20as%20she%20might%20be%20able%20to%20breath%20some%20life%20into%20the%20party%20while%20cultivating%20her%20own%20political%20ambition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20tipped%20to%20be%20either%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20or%20made%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20to%20look%20after%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20She%20was%20also%20reportedly%20sounded%20out%20for%20membership%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-revanth-reddy-optics-accessible-chief-minister%5C%22%3ETelangana%3A%20Revanth%20Reddy%20Gets%20the%20Optics%20Right%2C%20Cuts%20an%20Image%20of%20Accessible%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%20told%20media%20persons%20before%20leaving%20for%20Delhi%20that%20her%20YSR%20Telangana%20aided%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20by%20withdrawing%20from%20contest.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20Congress%20won%2031%20out%20of%20its%20total%20tally%20of%2064%20seats%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20less%20than%2010%2C000%20votes%20proves%20her%20point.%20Otherwise%2C%20YSR%20Telangana%20would%20likely%20have%20pulled%20all%20those%20votes%2C%20denying%20victory%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESharmila%20had%20extended%20unconditional%20support%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20after%20meeting%20Congress%20veteran%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20former%20party%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20She%20recalled%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20Congress%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20she%20backed%20out%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20defeat%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EShe%20had%20dropped%20hints%20of%20merging%20her%20party%20with%20the%20Congress%20but%20there%20was%20no%20confirmation%20until%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EA%20senior%20political%20figure%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20said%20that%20Sharmila%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20platform%20to%20counter%20her%20brother%20ever%20since%20she%20was%20denied%20her%20rightful%20share%20in%20YSR%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EShe%20had%20campaigned%20for%20the%20party%20in%20the%20elections%20and%20taken%20up%20a%203%2C100%20km%20long%20%3Cem%3Epadayatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Jagan%20after%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20jail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20a%20decade%20ago.%20She%20also%20led%20the%20party%20to%20victory%20in%2015%20out%20of%20the%2018%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20that%20went%20to%20by-elections%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EBut%20Jagan%20had%20not%20recognised%20her%20contribution%20and%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20set%20up%20obstacles%20in%20her%20path%20after%20assuming%20power.%20Sharmila%E2%80%99s%20husband%20and%20evangelist%20Brother%20Anil%20was%20quoted%20as%20telling%20a%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20leader%20B.%20Tech%20Ravi%20in%20a%20flight%20from%20Kadapa%20to%20Vijayawada%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20his%20wife%20was%20not%20at%20all%20interested%20in%20Andhra%20Pradrsh%20politics%20but%20took%20a%20plunge%20in%20it%20due%20to%20the%20hardship%20created%20by%20Jagan.%20B.%20Tech%20Ravi%20is%20former%20MLC%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Brother%20Anil%20was%20heading%20to%20Vijayawada%20to%20extended%20an%20invitation%20for%20the%20wedding%20of%20their%20son%20to%20Jagan%20and%20his%20wife.%20Sharmila%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20with%20Jagan%20lasted%20a%20mere%2015%20minutes%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Tadepalli%20near%20Vijayawada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EBrother%20Anil%20reportedly%20told%20B.%20Tech%20Ravi%20that%20Sharmila%20always%20felt%20it%20was%20not%20right%20for%20her%20to%20dabble%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20politics%20when%20her%20brother%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Therefore%2C%20she%20maintained%20a%20distance.%20But%20it%20had%20become%20inevitable%20for%20her%20to%20join%20politics%20in%20the%20state%20due%20to%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EY.S.%20Sharmila%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20politician%2C%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20Sharmila%20wanted%20a%20political%20party%20as%20a%20launchpad%20to%20nurse%20her%20ambition.%20That%20was%20how%20she%20floated%20the%20party%20in%20Telangana%20and%20took%20up%20a%203%2C800%20km%20%3Cem%3Epadayatra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20her%20second%20walkathon%2C%20which%20received%20good%20public%20response.%20This%20was%20despite%20knowing%20that%20there%20was%20no%20political%20space%20for%20her%20in%20Telangana%20as%20she%20had%20roots%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20When%20a%20party%20like%20TDP%20was%20wiped%20out%20in%20the%20political%20landscape%20of%20Telangana%2C%20there%20was%20hardly%20anything%20that%20she%20could%20achieve%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20referred%20to%20the%20pattern%20in%20a%20democratic%20set%20up%20of%20a%20ruling%20party%2C%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20and%20a%20third%20party%20that%20could%20step%20in%20if%20the%20latter%20failed%20to%20deliver.%20The%20exception%20to%20the%20norm%20could%20be%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20strong%20sub-regional%20party%20or%20a%20caste-based%20party%20that%20could%20alter%20the%20matrix.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20there%20was%20no%20way%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20could%20overtake%20Congress%20or%20the%20BJP%20to%20challenge%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20TDP%20was%20so%20strong%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20that%20there%20was%20no%20place%20either%20for%20BJP%20or%20Congress.%20The%20people%20had%20rejected%20Congress%20post-bifurcation%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20as%20they%20strongly%20believed%20that%20the%20party%20had%20conceded%20to%20Telangana%20at%20their%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ETelakapalli%20Ravi%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20said%20Sharmila%E2%80%99s%20entry%20in%20Congress%20could%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20embarrassment%20for%20Jagan%20politically%20because%20she%20was%20throwing%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20their%20father%20inherited%20by%20her%20brother.%20She%20was%20adding%20on%20to%20the%20wave%20of%20anti-incumbency%20faced%20by%20the%20TDP%20which%20is%20already%20suffering%20after%20the%20party%20extended%20its%20hand%20of%20friendship%20to%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20headed%20by%20actor%20turned%20politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20Jagan%20must%20be%20happy%20that%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote%20will%20be%20split%20if%20Congress%20gains%20due%20to%20its%20bond%20with%20Sharmila.%20It%20will%20also%20expose%20the%20double%20or%20%E2%80%98triple%E2%80%99%20standard%20of%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20already%20tied%20up%20with%20Jana%20Sena%20as%20partners%20in%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20entering%20into%20an%20understanding%20with%20the%20TDP%20to%20dislodge%20YSR%20Congress.%20This%20was%20some%20kind%20of%20an%20arrangement%20on%20the%20same%20lines%20as%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ERavi%20also%20said%20Sharmila%20will%20be%20adding%20a%20sentimental%20touch%20to%20the%20family%20moorings%20in%20the%20Congress%20carrying%20the%20image%20of%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20national%20media%20advisor%20to%20AP%20government%20Amar%20Devulapalli%20said%20Congress%20roped%20in%20Sharmila%20to%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20Jagan%20using%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20image%20but%20the%20party%20was%20decimated%20and%20there%20was%20no%20way%20it%20could%20make%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EProfessor%20K.%20Nageswar%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%2C%20said%20damage%20will%20be%20done%20to%20YSR%20Congress%20even%20if%20Sharmila%20could%20lead%20the%20Congress%20to%20wean%20away%20a%20small%20chunk%20of%20votes%20from%20the%20former%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C