th%20the%20federal%20level%20and%20provincial%20level.%20These%20administrations%20are%20constitutionally%20illegal%20because%20elections%20were%20not%20held%20within%2090%20days%20of%20parliamentary%20assemblies%20being%20dissolved%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20wrote%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20public%20is%20hearing%20that%20elections%20will%20supposedly%20be%20held%20on%20February%208th.%20But%20having%20been%20denied%20the%20same%20in%20two%20provinces%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20over%20the%20past%20year%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpakistan-top-court-rules-provincial-polls-delay-illegal-orders-voting-2023-04-04%2F%5C%22%3Eorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20March%20that%20those%20votes%20should%20be%20held%20within%20three%20months%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20right%20to%20be%20sceptical%20about%20whether%20the%20national%20vote%20will%20take%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20criticises%20the%20tainted%20actions%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Election%20Commission%2C%20alleging%20bias%20against%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20has%20it%20%5Bthe%20Election%20Commission%5D%20defied%20the%20top%20court%20but%20it%20has%20also%20rejected%20my%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%C2%A0%20party%E2%80%99s%20nominations%20for%20first-choice%20candidates%2C%20hindered%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20internal%20elections%20and%20launched%20contempt%20cases%20against%20me%20and%20other%20PTI%20leaders%20for%20simply%20criticising%20the%20commission%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20elections%20happen%20or%20not%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20I%20and%20my%20party%20have%20been%20targeted%20since%20a%20farcical%20vote%20of%20no%20confidence%20in%20April%202022%20has%20made%20one%20thing%20clear%3A%20the%20establishment%20%E2%80%93%20the%20army%2C%20security%20agencies%20and%20the%20civil%20bureaucracy%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20prepared%20to%20provide%20any%20playing%20field%20at%20all%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20level%20one%2C%20for%20PTI.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20the%20establishment%2C%20including%20the%20army%20and%20security%20agencies%2C%20of%20orchestrating%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20removal%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20mentioned%20the%20alleged%20American%20interference%20attempt%20through%20a%20State%20Department%20official%E2%80%99s%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20March%202022%2C%20an%20official%20from%20America%E2%80%99s%20State%20Department%20met%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20then%20ambassador%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20After%20that%20meeting%2C%20the%20ambassador%20sent%20a%20cipher%20message%20to%20my%20government.%20I%20later%20saw%20the%20message%2C%20via%20the%20then%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Shah%20Mahmood%20Qureshi%2C%20and%20it%20was%20subsequently%20read%20out%20in%20cabinet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20what%20the%20cipher%20message%20said%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20American%20official%E2%80%99s%20message%20was%20to%20the%20effect%20of%3A%20pull%20the%20plug%20on%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministership%20through%20a%20vote%20of%20no%20confidence%2C%20or%20else.%20Within%20weeks%20our%20government%20was%20toppled%20and%20I%20discovered%20that%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%2C%20had%2C%20through%20the%20security%20agencies%2C%20been%20working%20on%20our%20allies%20and%20parliamentary%20backbenchers%20for%20several%20months%20to%20move%20against%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20that%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20America%E2%80%99s%20State%20Department%20deny%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20of%20American%20interference%20in%20Pakistani%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20piece%2C%20he%20recounted%20public%20protests%20against%20the%20regime%20change%2C%20subsequent%20electoral%20victories%20in%20by-elections%2C%20and%20economic%20challenges%20under%20the%20new%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20highlights%20personal%20and%20party%20hardships%2C%20including%20assassination%20attempts%2C%20abductions%2C%20and%20legal%20persecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20the%20establishment%20had%20decided%20I%20could%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20return%20to%20power%2C%20so%20all%20means%20of%20removing%20me%20from%20the%20political%20landscape%20were%20used.%20There%20were%20two%20assassination%20attempts%20on%20my%20life.%20My%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%2C%20workers%20and%20social-media%20activists%2C%20along%20with%20supportive%20journalists%2C%20were%20abducted%2C%20incarcerated%2C%20tortured%20and%20pressured%20to%20leave%20pti.%20Many%20of%20them%20remain%20locked%20up%2C%20with%20new%20charges%20being%20thrown%20at%20them%20every%20time%20the%20courts%20give%20them%20bail%20or%20set%20them%20free.%20Worse%2C%20the%20current%20government%20has%20gone%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20terrorise%20and%20intimidate%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20female%20leaders%20and%20workers%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20discourage%20women%20from%20participating%20in%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20he%20advocated%20for%20fair%20and%20free%20elections%20as%20the%20only%20solution%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20viable%20way%20forward%20for%20Pakistan%20is%20fair%20and%20free%20elections%2C%20which%20would%20bring%20back%20political%20stability%20and%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ushering%20in%20desperately%20needed%20reforms%20by%20a%20democratic%20government%20with%20a%20popular%20mandate.%20There%20is%20no%20other%20way%20for%20Pakistan%20to%20disentangle%20itself%20from%20the%20crises%20confronting%20it.%20Unfortunately%2C%20with%20democracy%20under%20siege%2C%20we%20are%20heading%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20on%20all%20these%20fronts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704378518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F14222330%2FScreenshot-2023-03-14-at-10.22.49-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-election-could-be-a-farce-former-pm-imran-khan-writes-from-prison%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20prime%20minister%20accused%20the%20establishment%2C%20including%20the%20army%20and%20security%20agencies%2C%20of%20orchestrating%20his%20government's%20removal%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-election-could-be-a-farce-former-pm-imran-khan-writes-from-prison%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Renames%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20as%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F02122433%2Fimage-687.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20on%20Thursday%20(January%204)%20announced%20its%20decision%20to%20rename%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-leader-rahul-gandhi-to-start-bharat-nyay-yatra-on-january-14%5C%22%3EBharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20that%20will%20begin%20on%20January%2014%20from%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20will%20lead%20the%20march%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20from%20Imphal%20and%20end%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20March.%20The%20yatra%20will%20cover%20a%20total%20distance%20of%206%2C713%20kilometres%20across%20110%20districts%20in%20eastern%20and%20western%20India%20over%2066%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20map%20released%20by%20the%20party%2C%20th